➜北京望京凯悦酒店斩获ISO22000和GBAC资质认证
http://www.sohu.com/a/434905342_100116241	13015
<p>员工和宾客的健康与安全一直是北京望京凯悦酒店一路走来秉承的初心，在疫情期间更是顺理成章地成为了所有工作的重中之重。鉴于现阶段疫情的持续性，酒店将所有涉及员工和宾客安全的区域进行了全范围的重新评估，以“安全先行，健康相随”为宗旨，将优化后的规章和制度坚决贯彻执行到底。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">Caring for the safety and wellbeing of associates and guests during the coronavirus (COVID-19) outbreak is a top priority for Hyatt Regency Beijing Wangjing. As COVID-19 remains a dynamic situation, the hotel is taking comprehensive steps to implement new guidance, procedures and practices to reinvent the hotel experience for its associates and guests.</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201128/e74a851659904c19933517ef81c7ae0d.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>为了确保每一位员工和宾客都能切身感受到“安全先行，健康相随”的环境，在投入了持续性的人力、物力、精力后，酒店在过去的两个月内先后斩获ISO22000食品安全管理体系证书和GBAC资质。额外地健康和安全的种种措施在以“安全先行”为前提的境遇下全力推行，例如：减小接触、增加医用标准式消毒的频率，并使用手动式喷雾对员工和宾客能接触到的所有区域进行全方位定期监测。酒店在每位宾客预抵之前，都会对要入住的客房采取相应的关爱行动。在保持高质量的入住体验感的同时，对客房内的装饰及客用品进行重新规划并减少无关物品的摆放，高接触区域或物品也同时会被额外地照顾到。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">To ensure associates and guests feel confident that everything the hotel does is with the safety and wellbeing in mind. The hotel worked diligently to obtain accreditations from independent international organizations for Food Safety and Facilities Disinfection through ISO 22000 and the Global Biorisk Advisory Council recently. Additional health and safety measures are also being implemented, such as touch-free menu options, sanitization stations with hospital-grade disinfectants more frequently, and exploring and testing the use of electrostatic sprayers. Guestrooms are prepared with care in mind before every guests’ arrival. Guestroom décor and amenities have been enhanced to remove extraneous items while still providing high-quality experience.</p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
